description:
Cameron Adams is one hot stud. He has a quiet strength and rarely gets worked up. When it comes to sex, Cameron likes it rough and dirty. This week's update marks Gianni Luca's first match with Naked Kombat. He has wrestled for other companies and thinks this will be a walk in the park. This is Cameron's second match. He knows it's not easy on NK and he's prepared. Out of the gates, Gianni is stunned by the aggression and stamina required here. Can he bounce back and make Cameron his bitch for the day?
PS: This is Cameron's second match. His first match against Martin Lorenzo will be posted in the near future.
title: Cameron Adams vs Gianni Luca
